extraction:
{
    "raw_text": "ひろし
おい、顔出すなよ
リモートワーク中だからな",
    "translation": "Hiroshi
Hey, don't show your face
Because I'm in the middle of remote work"
}

{
    "raw_text": "カズコ
...いや、別になんでもないんです！
なにかご用ですか？",
    "translation": "Kazuko
...No, it's nothing really!
Do you need something?"
}

{
    "raw_text": "みさえ
しんちゃん、でかけるときは
声かけてから行くのよ～",
    "translation": "Misae:
Shin-chan, when you go out,
let me know before you leave~"
}

{
    "raw_text": "つる
はたけ あいじょう
畑はな、愛情をかければかけるほど
やさい つく
んめぇー野菜を作ってくれんだ～",
    "translation": "Tsuru:
The field... the more love you give it,
The more delicious vegetables it will grow for you~"
}

{
    "raw_text": "つる
ばあちゃんが見てやっから
野菜の収穫がんばってみるか？",
    "translation": "Tsuru
Grandma will watch over you
Want to try your best at harvesting vegetables?"
}

{
    "raw_text": "ヤマオ
やあ、しんのすけくん！
なにか買っていくかい？",
    "translation": "Yamao
Hey, Shinnosuke!
Would you like to buy something?"
}
